headline: 3 Hypergrowth Tech Stocks to Buy in 2025
summary: Throw in the fact that artificial intelligence (AI) is fueling speculation in tech stocks, and things become even cloudier.  Nvidia's (NASDAQ: NVDA) leading position in artificial intelligence semiconductors cannot be overstated.  The company holds an estimated 70% to 95% of the AI semiconductor market, and Nvidia's strong third quarter (which ended Oct. 27) proved this AI juggernaut isn't slowing down.
